350
00:25:52,420 --> 00:25:55,340
 Znači, to je ko SDP da vlada, ne znam, visom.

351
00:25:55,340 --> 00:25:58,100
 Dalje je to Kina, iako SDP tamo vlada.

352
00:25:58,100 --> 00:25:59,040
 Hrvatska, pardon.

353
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:01,480
 Dobro, shvatila sam, shvatila sam.

354
00:26:01,480 --> 00:26:05,080
 Znači, oni će biti najveći dobitnik, oni rastu u megasilu,

355
00:26:05,080 --> 00:26:08,840
